<paragraph id="D7A7D11624A08641B419AA4986E641A3" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5610187EB74A0DDE8693902DB4D33872" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<bibRefCitation id="C64B76D2C6E16D2D1A13AD8882AAEFB6" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1111/syen.12460" author="Benda, D" journalOrPublisher="Systematic Entomology" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="252 - 265" refId="B4" refString="Benda, D, Votypkova, K, Nakase, Y, Straka, J, 2021. Unexpected cryptic species diversity of parasites of the family Xenidae (Strepsiptera) with a constant diversification rate over time. Systematic Entomology 46: 252 - 265, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1111/syen.12460" title="Unexpected cryptic species diversity of parasites of the family Xenidae (Strepsiptera) with a constant diversification rate over time." url="https://doi.org/10.1111/syen.12460" volume="46" year="2021">Benda et al. (2021)</bibRefCitation>
proposed at least four distinctive 
<taxonomicName id="E48725658B8C6302D101DB63279CEE53" genus="T." lsidName="T. sphecidarum" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="species" species="sphecidarum">
